    "name": "Nuclear Mages",
    "steam_appid": 2195190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Developers quote: &quot; Diablo 2 meets Skyrim in a epic tale with its own lore ! &quot;</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/cf544c936b79be5f58743d0b868cdf57.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=80 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/47f384304ec7c47b609677d6e5767ca6.poster.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/47f384304ec7c47b609677d6e5767ca6.webm?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/47f384304ec7c47b609677d6e5767ca6.mp4?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Harnessing the power of elemental magic, you select your affinity </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >among the primordial forces: fire, water, earth, wind—</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the realm of Everdawn, the ancient threat known as the Void looms ominously, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >seeking to engulf the world in eternal chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a chosen wielder of light and arcane energies, you embark on a perilous quest to thwart this malevolent force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roaming through diverse landscapes, your presence stirs the dormant darkness, forcing its sinister denizens to materialize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/80877ed3a5b69126cdb58fde3e9180af.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=80 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/74dbca0705b51464621ea3c6972f5ca8.poster.avif?t=1729685856\" width=340 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/74dbca0705b51464621ea3c6972f5ca8.webm?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/74dbca0705b51464621ea3c6972f5ca8.mp4?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In battle, each vanquished foe releases shimmering Void orbs, relics brimming with corrupted energy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By aiding the enigmatic seer Zara, a guardian of ancient wisdom, you unlock the secrets of these orbs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zara's guidance empowers you with passive skills and insights, purchased through the harmonious synthesis of light and Void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an expedition through the vast expanse of the Town map, a sprawling zone </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >teeming with otherworldly wonders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each corner of this mysterious realm unveils unique worlds adorned with fantastical flora </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and eccentric fungi, a testament to the realm's enigmatic history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/d530c16c725e15929fff9337f23e4925.poster.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/d530c16c725e15929fff9337f23e4925.webm?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/d530c16c725e15929fff9337f23e4925.mp4?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amidst your exploration, encounter five peculiar shops offering exotic wares and arcane </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >artifacts essential for your quest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Safeguard your discoveries within the confines of your home chest, the sole sanctuary in </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >this unpredictable landscape where treasures remain secure against the encroaching chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To expand your storage capacity, seek out ancient runes scattered across the land. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>These mystical items serve as enchanted pouches, enhancing your ability to safeguard </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>and organize your burgeoning collection of relics and curiosities.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture deeper into the world, find ancient ruins, long forgotten by time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot these venerable sites to uncover relics of immense power and untold secrets, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >piecing together the cryptic tapestry of Everdawn's past while fortifying your resolve against </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >the encroaching Void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>** Magic Only **</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>**No weapons**</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/9df6ce932bd51ad37cbeb2691301ede6.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=80 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/ae92a33a900d5475b85a6225a537aa9b.poster.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/ae92a33a900d5475b85a6225a537aa9b.webm?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/ae92a33a900d5475b85a6225a537aa9b.mp4?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delve into a realm of endless gear combinations and unique traits, where every choice shapes your destiny!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/be5429fc96701c15eab82f1e87357771.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=80 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/846ee53d0b0d658cd3dce04372d14868.poster.avif?t=1729685856\" width=300 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/846ee53d0b0d658cd3dce04372d14868.webm?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/846ee53d0b0d658cd3dce04372d14868.mp4?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thus, armed with elemental prowess and guided by ancient wisdom, you venture forth </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >into the heart of Everdawn to cleanse the land of the encroaching shadows and restore </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >balance to a world on the brink of oblivion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend into treacherous dungeons, where each step brings peril and potential. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In these shadowed depths, every defeat exacts a heavy toll:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>loss of precious loot and hard-earned passive skills.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yet, amid the danger lies unparalleled opportunity for gear progression, with each delve yielding </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >rare materials vital for enhancing your power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A special merchant is hidden in the caverns on the HARD and INSANE dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hidden merchants offer's items crucial to gear progression.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/a189f8226ff03b35275000473ee70d8c.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=80 /></span>Harness the ancient arts of crafting and alchemy at specialized stations strewn across the realm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of potion brewing, where the initial refining process yields a bountiful harvest, providing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >an invaluable advantage in your quest against the encroaching Void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize the spoils of your conquests to fashion bespoke gear, each piece a testament to your prowess </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and resilience. Merge the essence of your discoveries into formidable equipment, forging a legacy destined to defy chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft and refine potions at special stations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refining the first stage of potions yields twice the input.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through meticulous refinement, forge potent elixirs that can turn the tide of battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/83818f5589b10fba837ff6fe9a374e8b.poster.avif?t=1729685856\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/83818f5589b10fba837ff6fe9a374e8b.webm?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/83818f5589b10fba837ff6fe9a374e8b.mp4?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potion of uncertain demise of power: Drink this and get 7x damage multiplier for 2 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                              50% chance to die upon drinking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/cc5b25c1ef1fe729cd6583ea274e1aaa.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand firm against the onslaught, for the fate of Everdawn hangs in the balance. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only through cunning strategy and unwavering determination can you safeguard the sanctity of your crystal and </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >push back the relentless waves of the Void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon forth relentless waves of adversaries, drawn like moths to the flame of your unwavering resolve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the enemy masses converge upon your sanctuary, fortify its defences with a strategic array of towers, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >each a testament to your mastery of arcane engineering.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every tower built and upgraded, bolster the crystal's protection against the relentless tide of Void. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash the elemental energies at your command, infusing each structure with the power to repel and </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >vanquish the encroaching chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**Alpha has 1 tower model that can be upgraded x3.**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/70a9381c078e6681f27b8db9ce33866c.poster.avif?t=1729685856\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/70a9381c078e6681f27b8db9ce33866c.webm?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195190/extras/70a9381c078e6681f27b8db9ce33866c.mp4?t=1729685856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One Lane per map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the crystal gets hit by ONE enemy, you loose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full body physics; you can trip and fall. Be thrown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Same for enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First beginners guide<br><br>Check youtube link in the right steam panel<br>On top of Discord link</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*** Tutorial is 16 min. You will need minimum 1 hour of gameplay to NUKE ***</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alpha is solo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open world town map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Called Hall of heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shop keep that keeps player listings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 dungeons with each its unique boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extractor type dungeons with exit portals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower defence map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 waves to select from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 tower to build and upgrade x2</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Current state of game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Alpha*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*** One person studio ***</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Studio Promises:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will NEVER be or will NEVER have:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Pay to win</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Crypto infused</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- DLC packs extra $</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Paying for character storage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hidden Charges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Subscription Based.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Account levels. silver/gold...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beta will be Co-op 2-6 players per map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Destructible environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Mount system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Player driven economy.</p>",
